business, that it broke my back!

1161
01:59:58,216 --> 02:00:00,937
Somebody's profit, somebody's loss.

1162
02:00:01,464 --> 02:00:03,918
Somebody's loss is somebody's gain.

1163
02:00:04,444 --> 02:00:06,694
This is the world!

1164
02:00:07,617 --> 02:00:10,168
Today you had my factory shut down.

1165
02:00:11,374 --> 02:00:14,598
You grabbed all my workers, my talent.

1166
02:00:17,184 --> 02:00:18,181
Talent?

1167
02:00:19,605 --> 02:00:22,301
