snatched somebody's talent!

1168
02:00:23,892 --> 02:00:24,978
Laxminarayan!

1169
02:00:27,540 --> 02:00:29,067
I will be ruined Dad.

1170
02:00:30,085 --> 02:00:32,602
My blood and sweat too
is mingled in that business.

1171
02:00:33,228 --> 02:00:35,481
At least think of my future.

1172
02:00:36,122 --> 02:00:39,246
I have no interest in anyone's future!

1173
02:00:41,081 --> 02:00:42,597
Mr. Chander Kishen...

1174
02:00:43,628 --> 02:00:47,028
