After every kind of inquiry,
it has been proved...

1178
02:01:18,323 --> 02:01:20,622
..that Ramesh has misappropriated
50000 rupees belonging to the bank!

1179
02:01:20,834 --> 02:01:24,559
This is wrong. I did nothing.

1180
02:01:24,903 --> 02:01:26,850
I did not misappropriate funds.

1181
02:01:27,159 --> 02:01:30,098
I am innocent!

1182
02:01:30,545 --> 02:01:32,004
That will be decided by the court.

1183
02:01:32,307 --> 02:01:33,901
You are under arrest, Mr. Ramesh.

1184
02:01:33,989 --> 02:01:34,473
Sir.

1185
02:01:34,514 --> 02:01:35,389
Tukaram.

1186
02:01:36,170 --> 02:01:37,014
Sir.

1187
02:01:51,828 --> 02:01:52,769
Daughter-in-law!

1188
02:01:55,317 --> 02:01:56,460
You and here?

1189
02:02:03,283 --> 02:02:07,481
Mother, I am ruined! A mountain
of difficulties fell on us!

1190
02:02:08,010 --> 02:02:10,434
The bank people acted mean with us.

1191
02:02:10,773 --> 02:02:14,700
They accused my husband of
misappropriation and had him arrested.

1192
02:02:15,056 --> 02:02:15,976
What?

1193
02:02:18,172 --> 02:02:21,859
Ramesh arrested!
Did you hear?

1194
02:02:24,490 --> 02:02:25,652
I am listening.

1195
02:02:28,231 --> 02:02:33,214
What's surprising about it?

1196
02:02:34,192 --> 02:02:37,317
He is innocent. He has been framed.

1197
02:02:38,562 --> 02:02:40,465
Save him father!

1198
02:02:41,373 --> 02:02:44,622
Or he will be imprisoned!
We will be destroyed!

1199
02:02:46,173 --> 02:02:49,012
Nobody supports criminals.

1200
02:02:50,178 --> 02:02:51,848
You've come to the wrong door.

1201
02:02:59,410 --> 02:03:02,194
Mother, please do something.

1202
02:03:02,465 --> 02:03:05,101
Pay the bail and save your son.

1203
02:03:10,122 --> 02:03:11,425
Come with me.

1204
02:03:21,125 --> 02:03:22,025
Radha...

1205
02:03:24,255 --> 02:03:26,503
You won't pay the bail.

1206
02:03:29,168 --> 02:03:30,936
I bind you by oath!

1207
02:04:16,744 --> 02:04:17,549
Sir...

1208
02:04:19,466 --> 02:04:21,840
This is between you and me.

1209
02:04:22,080 --> 02:04:26,012
Don't worry, I will pay
bail for Ramesh tomorrow morning.

1210
02:04:26,666 --> 02:04:28,825
What is the need for money?

1211
02:04:29,661 --> 02:04:30,984
There is need.

1212
02:04:31,957 --> 02:04:34,166
I don't trust Ramesh at all.

1213
02:04:35,444 --> 02:04:42,497
And I'm not paying this bail for
Ramesh but for the sake of Radha.

1214
02:04:43,910 --> 02:04:48,793
