Dad and Mom are here to meet you.

1253
02:08:07,710 --> 02:08:10,544
- Greetings, father!
- Greetings, father!

1254
02:08:12,173 --> 02:08:15,084
How did you come here?

1255
02:08:16,164 --> 02:08:17,197
Is everything fine?

1256
02:08:18,022 --> 02:08:23,108
Dad, you left home and happiness
and prosperity left with you.

1257
02:08:25,202 --> 02:08:29,702
If we made a mistake,
please overlook it.

1258
02:08:31,733 --> 02:08:33,959
May the Lord punish me!

1259
02:08:34,222 --> 02:08:39,201
If one cruel word escapes my lips,
you may pull out my tongue!

1260
02:08:39,818 --> 02:08:44,803
For the sake of God, spit out
your anger and come back home!

1261
02:08:45,806 --> 02:08:50,420
To grind flour?
To wash clothes? To be scolded?

1262
02:08:50,508 --> 02:08:54,012
- I swear by God...
- Don't take false promises.

1263
02:08:54,426 --> 02:08:57,084
You'll face the Almighty
with the face of a pig!

1264
02:08:57,723 --> 02:09:01,311
Hen-pecked! You ruined
everything for one woman!

1265
02:09:01,368 --> 02:09:01,988
Father...

1266
02:09:02,029 --> 02:09:03,833
Wipe those crocodile tears!

1267
02:09:04,420 --> 02:09:08,336
I understand everything.
This is the miracle of money!

1268
02:09:08,769 --> 02:09:12,433
My Provident Fund is
dripping down your eyes!

1269
02:09:13,187 --> 02:09:16,209
As if it's a bone not cash,
that you smelt and came here!

1270
02:09:16,821 --> 02:09:20,286
Hear this carefully!
You won't get a single penny!

1271
02:09:21,379 --> 02:09:24,236
Don't be so cruel-hearted!

1272
02:09:24,277 --> 02:09:26,531
Take her away from my sight!

1273
02:09:27,021 --> 02:09:29,794
The Rashid who lived off your
leftovers is dead and gone!

1274
02:09:32,204 --> 02:09:36,177
Keep one thing in mind, God forbid...

1275
02:09:36,658 --> 02:09:39,685
...if your son throws you out of the
house when he grows...

1276
02:09:40,160 --> 02:09:44,340
...come here with my name.
You'll get place to stay.

1277
02:10:03,587 --> 02:10:08,317
We've interviewed you.
We'll let you know later.

1278
02:10:08,576 --> 02:10:09,353
Thank you, sir.

1279
02:10:09,865 --> 02:10:10,481
Next.

1280
02:10:13,359 --> 02:10:14,942
- Good morning, sir.
- Good morning.

1281
02:10:15,623 --> 02:10:17,206
Your name?

1282
02:10:17,323 --> 02:10:18,732
Ramesh Kishen.

1283
02:10:19,436 --> 02:10:20,990
- Age?
- 26 years.

1284
02:10:21,953 --> 02:10:26,029
- .Qualifications.
- Cheating, deception.

1285
02:10:27,045 --> 02:10:30,841
Swindling, craftiness,
misappropriation.

1286
02:10:31,078 --> 02:10:32,926
- Father.
- Mr. Gupta...

1287
02:10:33,333 --> 02:10:37,262
We don't want such a qualified
and educated man for this Job!

1288
02:10:38,124 --> 02:10:39,214
Father.

1289
02:11:07,759 --> 02:11:08,607
Chander!

1290
02:11:12,036 --> 02:11:15,814
- What is this?
- He is in difficulty.

1291
02:11:15,870 --> 02:11:17,706
I want to help him.

1292
02:11:17,863 --> 02:11:22,068
If you want to help them do it
with money earned yourself!

1293
02:11:22,572 --> 02:11:26,161
Our money is not for charity!
That you distribute to beggars!

1294
02:11:26,257 --> 02:11:29,513
Aren't you ashamed to insult them?

1295
02:11:29,648 --> 02:11:32,865
You should be ashamed.
You've started stealing!

1296
02:11:33,078 --> 02:11:38,075
- You're crossing all limits!
- You are crossing limits not me!

1297
02:11:38,597 --> 02:11:41,951
Don't quarrel because of us.

1298
02:11:42,387 --> 02:11:45,769
We came to you as we're family.

1299
02:11:45,982 --> 02:11:47,974
I hate family!

1300
02:11:48,316 --> 02:11:52,482
Go away from here.
I don't want to see your faces!

1301
02:12:00,838 --> 02:12:05,959
- This was very bad!
- No it was good!

1302
02:12:06,940 --> 02:12:08,917
Shut your mouth!

1303
02:12:09,460 --> 02:12:11,300
I've been tolerating you for long!

1304
02:12:11,880 --> 02:12:15,638
If you want to live off us,
you'll have to put up with more!

1305
02:12:15,700 --> 02:12:18,358
- Renu!
- Shameless! How dare you!

1306
02:12:19,031 --> 02:12:22,286
See how unjustly she behaved me!

1307
02:12:22,699 --> 02:12:25,435
- I'm her husband!
- I made the same mistake.

1308
02:12:26,154 --> 02:12:29,476
Money can change the
clothes not the body!

1309
02:12:29,594 --> 02:12:31,238
You are right.

1310
02:12:31,834 --> 02:12:34,997
Your father earned some money
and forgot himself and his place!

1311
02:12:35,431 --> 02:12:38,880
he blocked our means of livelihood!
And you're responsible for it!

1312
02:12:39,131 --> 02:12:42,904
- What's my fault?
- The fault is of the cheap blood!

1313
02:12:44,089 --> 02:12:46,700
The way your scoundrel of a
father behaved with us..

1314
02:12:47,234 --> 02:12:50,982
I should have thrown you out
of the house at seeing that!

1315
02:12:52,421 --> 02:12:55,357
But I'm not depraved.
I won't do that.

1316
02:12:55,967 --> 02:13:02,055
But you may leave if you want to.
The door is open. Come dear.

1317
02:13:15,567 --> 02:13:19,301
Two bars of Lux, one cream
and one toothpaste.

1318
02:13:19,342 --> 02:13:23,011
Excuse me first clear the old account.

1319
02:13:23,535 --> 02:13:27,848
It's been 3 whole months.
You owe me 450 rupees.

1320
02:13:29,062 --> 02:13:31,504
I'll clear the debt. Trust me.

1321
02:13:32,721 --> 02:13:35,207
The days of trust have gone sir.

1322
02:13:36,234 --> 02:13:39,262
These days I'm little hard pressed.

1323
02:13:39,939 --> 02:13:42,762
I'm not running a factory.
I have a small business.

1324
02:13:42,849 --> 02:13:47,004
If everyone takes credit,
my whole business will flop!

1325
02:13:47,169 --> 02:13:50,676
- But...
- I will give no credit now!

1326
02:13:51,058 --> 02:13:53,705
Times change a bit and you turn away!

1327
02:13:53,942 --> 02:13:56,879
have you forgotten you've taken
thousands of rupees from these hands?

1328
02:13:57,151 --> 02:14:00,933
But in return for goods.
That was not charity!

1329
02:14:01,273 --> 02:14:02,731
Neither have you done me any favours!

1330
02:14:02,947 --> 02:14:06,319
When I don't have money, you stop
giving credit! Is this decency?

1331
02:14:06,485 --> 02:14:09,311
I know how decent you are!

1332
02:14:09,352 --> 02:14:13,225
Have you forgotten it was you who...

1333
02:14:13,324 --> 02:14:15,435
...closed your Dad's cigarette
credit when he fell on bad times?

1334
02:14:15,500 --> 02:14:16,543
Ramdulare!

1335
02:15:58,014 --> 02:15:58,751
Kishen...

1336
02:16:00,849 --> 02:16:01,891
Forgive them.

1337
02:16:03,285 --> 02:16:05,030
It is your own who are forgiven.

1338
02:16:07,603 --> 02:16:08,772
I have forgotten them.

1339
02:16:11,510 --> 02:16:12,724
I can't forget.

1340
02:16:17,059 --> 02:16:20,707
My children ...will stay with me.

1341
02:16:21,318 --> 02:16:22,537
That's impossible!

1342
02:16:22,780 --> 02:16:27,217
Why not? Don't I have any worth,
any respect in your eyes?

1343
02:16:27,258 --> 02:16:28,894
Can't I do anything?

1344
02:16:29,439 --> 02:16:32,850
Who was your partner in Joy
and sorrow? It was me.

1345
02:16:33,555 --> 02:16:36,780
I walked with you with a heavy heart.

1346
02:16:37,519 --> 02:16:39,662
I never turned to look at the kids.

1347
02:16:40,422 --> 02:16:44,240
Because I had the assurance that
they are happy where they are.

1348
02:16:44,824 --> 02:16:47,708
But today they are homeless,
with no support.

1349
02:16:48,151 --> 02:16:49,491
They are broken in every way.

1350
02:16:49,568 --> 02:16:54,311
Whom are you mourning for? The ones
who're perpetual wounds for parents?

1351
02:16:55,023 --> 02:16:57,523
They cannot stay in my house!

1352
02:16:58,601 --> 02:17:01,990
This is also my house!
I too have some right over it!

1353
02:17:02,535 --> 02:17:05,757
You have a right
over my body and soul.

1354
02:17:06,496 --> 02:17:11,209
You are everywhere but I have
no place for your maternal love!

1355
02:17:12,418 --> 02:17:15,428
Because today you have name!

1356
02:17:16,476 --> 02:17:18,790
You have been blinded by
the glitter of wealth!

1357
02:17:19,164 --> 02:17:20,923
So blind that you can't
see your own blood!

1358
02:17:21,911 --> 02:17:26,314
Don't be so cruel!
They are repenting for their deeds.

1359
02:17:26,788 --> 02:17:30,645
And even God forgives all sins
for one tear of repentance!

1360
02:17:31,882 --> 02:17:33,636
I am not God!

1361
02:17:36,921 --> 02:17:37,862
Kishen!

1362
02:17:43,086 --> 02:17:46,950
One day you said I never
asked you for anything in life.

1363
02:17:47,744 --> 02:17:49,722
And I said I will ask for it
when the time comes.

1364
02:17:50,535 --> 02:17:54,098
And you said you'd wait for that day.

1365
02:17:56,764 --> 02:17:58,950
The day has come.

1366
02:18:04,625 --> 02:18:06,878
Give me my children!

1367
02:18:21,241 --> 02:18:23,029
- Hello.
- Kishen...

1368
02:18:24,108 --> 02:18:26,887
It's quite late.
You're still in the office.

1369
02:18:28,491 --> 02:18:29,791
When are you coming home?

1370
02:18:30,666 --> 02:18:35,193
I may not be able to come home.

1371
02:18:36,563 --> 02:18:39,733
I have an important meeting going on.

1372
02:20:13,756 --> 02:20:14,656
Kishen!

1373
02:20:22,007 --> 02:20:27,069
You came here in this storm?

1374
02:20:27,852 --> 02:20:30,116
No storm could stop me today!

1375
02:20:31,768 --> 02:20:33,998
Why aren't you coming home?

1376
02:20:36,769 --> 02:20:39,788
There's no time. Work has increased.

1377
02:20:41,048 --> 02:20:44,380
Work hasn't increased.
It has got spoilt.

1378
02:20:44,863 --> 02:20:49,217
Whom are you making excuses to?
Showing this anger? To me?

1379
02:20:50,834 --> 02:20:54,858
You know I don't get angry.

1380
02:20:56,292 --> 02:21:00,358
It would be better if you would.
You could hit me and be relieved!

1381
02:21:00,633 --> 02:21:04,686
I would be at peace!
But why are you burning me within?

1382
02:21:08,452 --> 02:21:10,234
What are you saying?

1383
02:21:10,554 --> 02:21:12,684
I know you better than I know myself.

1384
02:21:13,312 --> 02:21:16,355
I supported my children
so you left my side!

1385
02:21:16,784 --> 02:21:18,506
You are punishing me so severely.

1386
02:21:23,464 --> 02:21:25,693
You couldn't spend a minute without me

1387
02:21:26,159 --> 02:21:30,037
Today it is 4 days and
I am tossing on live embers.

1388
02:21:30,148 --> 02:21:31,815
But you don't give a damn!

1389
02:21:32,504 --> 02:21:35,779
You broke all relations, gave up
your rights and came here.

1390
02:21:36,416 --> 02:21:39,771
I'm living for you.

1391
02:21:43,905 --> 02:21:46,140
You have enough people.

1392
02:21:47,438 --> 02:21:51,337
A thorn pricked your heart Just
because motherhood beckoned me!

1393
02:21:51,378 --> 02:21:52,836
And you're sulking with it.

1394
02:21:53,967 --> 02:21:56,952
Why don't you think of
the cross roads I am at?

1395
02:21:57,221 --> 02:21:59,873
Wherever I go, I am incomplete!

1396
02:22:00,143 --> 02:22:02,741
Even a stone would melt at my state!

1397
02:22:07,054 --> 02:22:10,694
But you are not even a stone!
You are a lifeless soul!

1398
02:22:11,427 --> 02:22:13,824
No love, emotions, feelings!

1399
02:22:13,896 --> 02:22:15,536
You have no heart!

1400
02:22:15,764 --> 02:22:18,466
You are heartless!

1401
02:22:27,223 --> 02:22:29,174
You have no heart!

1402
02:22:31,144 --> 02:22:32,445
You are heartless!

1403
02:22:34,539 --> 02:22:35,847
You are heartless!

1404
02:22:37,171 --> 02:22:38,790
You have no heart!

1405
02:22:40,240 --> 02:22:41,444
You are heartless!

1406
02:22:42,911 --> 02:22:44,482
You have no heart!

1407
02:22:44,551 --> 02:22:47,180
You are heartless!

1408
02:23:55,991 --> 02:23:59,457
Avtaar! Avtaar!

1409
02:24:03,929 --> 02:24:05,202
Come, sir!

1410
02:24:05,783 --> 02:24:07,904
Where is Avtaar?

1411
02:24:12,080 --> 02:24:14,463
What's the matter?
Is everything all right?

1412
02:24:15,297 --> 02:24:19,772
When we were with you,
we were really happy.

1413
02:24:20,836 --> 02:24:24,834
But now he's not the same.

1414
02:24:25,640 --> 02:24:29,920
He has changed totally.
Today he has forgotten me!

1415
02:24:29,961 --> 02:24:32,610
No! What are you saying?

1416
02:24:32,823 --> 02:24:36,773
He can forget himself not you.

1417
02:24:39,349 --> 02:24:42,250
I will always remember that night.

1418
02:24:43,858 --> 02:24:50,829
And I'm giving this bail
for Radha not Ramesh.

1419
02:24:52,196 --> 02:24:56,945
I can't bear to see my life cry.

1420
02:24:57,835 --> 02:24:58,804
What?

1421
02:25:00,452 --> 02:25:04,859
Meaning.. the bail was paid by..

1422
02:25:31,288 --> 02:25:31,866
Hello.

1423
02:25:32,426 --> 02:25:35,885
Mistress! Come fast!
Sir has suffered a stroke!

1424
02:26:11,703 --> 02:26:13,513
Forgive me.

1425
02:26:14,570 --> 02:26:16,155
Forgive me.

1426
02:26:17,750 --> 02:26:19,292
Don't cry silly.

1427
02:26:21,697 --> 02:26:23,140
I am fine.

1428
02:26:28,870 --> 02:26:29,747
Radha.

1429
02:26:34,290 --> 02:26:36,445
So far I was on duty.

1430
02:26:38,055 --> 02:26:42,279
Looks like it's time for me to retire.

1431
02:26:42,633 --> 02:26:47,492
Don't say that!

1432
02:27:19,413 --> 02:27:20,684
Radha...

1433
02:27:22,142 --> 02:27:24,000
I have only one request.

1434
02:27:26,253 --> 02:27:35,555
After me make one Apna Ghar
centre in every city of the country.

1435
02:27:36,656 --> 02:27:38,718
Make my dream come true.

1436
02:27:45,944 --> 02:27:49,343
From my property...

1437
02:27:50,468 --> 02:27:53,031
...I leave 2 lakhs to Ramesh Kishen.

1438
02:27:53,888 --> 02:27:57,101
And 2 lakhs to Chander Kishen.

1439
02:27:58,708 --> 02:28:02,195
Not because they are my sons.

1440
02:28:03,190 --> 02:28:10,594
But because their behaviour gave me
a new direction, showed me a new path.

1441
02:28:14,236 --> 02:28:18,442
Sewak, who all his life...

1442
02:28:19,405 --> 02:28:23,233
... served me selflessly.

1443
02:28:24,308 --> 02:28:28,552
I wish to put one
more burden on him.

1444
02:28:30,903 --> 02:28:34,146
If something happens to me..

1445
02:28:35,350 --> 02:28:36,709
Then my body should be...

1446
02:28:38,431 --> 02:28:42,062
...torched and cremated by Sewak.

1447
02:28:46,986 --> 02:28:48,225
Sir!

1448
02:28:51,045 --> 02:28:51,933
Sir.

1449
02:29:21,553 --> 02:29:30,243
"The world never stops moving."

1450
02:29:32,385 --> 02:29:39,089
"The world never stops moving."

1451
02:29:39,372 --> 02:29:46,145
"The world is a stage."

1452
02:29:46,365 --> 02:29:53,006
"Friends, bid me a cheerful farewell."

1453
02:29:53,298 --> 02:30:00,553
"Leave my hand and let me go now."

1454
02:30:03,969 --> 02:30:11,053
"Don't cry and break my promise."

1455
02:30:11,094 --> 02:30:17,881
"Leave my hand and let me go now."

1456
02:30:18,321 --> 02:30:21,670
"Leave my hand, friends."

1457
02:30:22,502 --> 02:30:25,456
"Friends."

